finds his fey eidolon, a dryad, in the rine of a banana (he's a banana farmer). Eventually he raises her as his daughter and she grows into an adorable woman. Problem is every time the half elf goes to sleep the eidolon is warped back to the First World, which she hates because of how terrifying it is. The two are out on an adventure to find a way to permanently bind the eidolon to this world.